# Launch toward the console, bounce away, then cross the lower track.
10-50: thrust
30-30: fire
60-60: fire

# Turn east while coasting toward the lower outer wall.
94-111: right

# Accelerate across the track toward the right wall and keep firing.
112-235: thrust
120-120: fire
150-150: fire
180-180: fire
210-210: fire

# Coast after the second outer-wall bounce so its flash can decay on camera.
